traditional N-body simulations. Increased tidal forces substantially alter\ncircular velocity profiles for satellites with pericentres less than 50 kpc. We\nshow that these two effects are strong enough to bring the predictions of\nsubhaloes from CDM simulations into agreement with the observed structure of MW\ndSphs, regardless of the details of the baryonic processes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 29 Dec 2012 18:00:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 11 Dec 2013 18:31:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
